      "file_path": "cps-service/src/main/java/org/onap/cps/utils/YangUtils.java",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 120,
      "message": "```\n    private void inspectLeafList(final DataNode currentDataNode, final LeafSetNode leafSetNode) {\n        final String leafName = leafSetNode.getNodeType().getLocalName();\n        final Set<Object> leafListValue = ImmutableSet.of(\n            ((Collection<NormalizedNode>) leafSetNode.getValue())\n                .stream().map(NormalizedNode::getValue).collect(Collectors.toSet())\n        );\n        cpsDataNodeBuilder.addLeafValue(leafName, leafListValue); // same method as for leafs\n    }\n```\nyou need just one (!) method, same one to set leaf value for both leaf and leaf-list nodes, \nthis will simplifies the logic significantly",
      "author": {
